<release version="0.2.2" date="2026-06-21">
  <description>
    <p>Added:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Auto-mute by @Arzumify in https://github.com/waywallen/waywallen/pull/110.</li>
      <li>Auto pause to Auto replay with mute and stop support.</li>
      <li>Support pause and mute fade.</li>
      <li>New lua plugin entry.</li>
      <li>Cosmic support.</li>
      <li>Custom resolution.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Fixes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Layershell display rotation.</li>
      <li>Web wallpaper init on nvidia card.</li>
      <li>Image frames replay after relinking displays to an existing image renderer.</li>
      <li>Renderer texture size reporting on the displays page.</li>
      <li>wallpapers loading component when filtered.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
</release>
